User story : 
- user dapat memberikan current lokasi
- user dapat melihat countdown timer (setelah imsyak sebelum buka) ($ > imsyak && $ < buka)
- user dapat melihat message after buka puasa ($ > buka && $ < imsyak)


Technical flow : 
- Get current location : lat, long
- konversi ke address -> city
- store to local as current location

initial
- Fetch data city 
- store to local
- Fetch data jadwal sholat by city and date (now)
- store to local 
- countdown (lib) by checking in local by day
